---
---

<footer class="bot">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="f-brand">
      <a href="/" class="brand"><span class="logo" aria-hidden="true"></span>연합우주</a>
      <p>작은 공동체들이 이어진 인터넷의 안내 페이지. 누구나 기여할 수 있는 공동의 문서입니다.</p>
    </div>
    <div>
      <h5>둘러보기</h5>
      <ul>
        <li><a href="/communities">커뮤니티 디렉토리</a></li>
        <li><a href="/faq">자주 묻는 질문</a></li>
        <li><a href="/contribute">기여하기</a></li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <div>
      <h5>프로젝트</h5>
      <ul>
        <li>
          <a href="https://github.com/fedidevkr/join-fediverse" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
            GitHub
          </a>
        </li>
        <li>
          <a
            href="https://github.com/fedidevkr/join-fediverse/blob/main/CONTRIBUTING.md"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener">기여 가이드</a
          >
        </li>
        <li>
          <a
            href="https://github.com/fedidevkr/join-fediverse/blob/main/LICENSE"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener">라이선스 · CC0</a
          >
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <div>
      <h5>더 읽기</h5>
      <ul>
        <li>
          <a href="https://www.w3.org/TR/activitypub/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">ActivityPub</a>
        </li>
        <li>
          <a href="https://joinmastodon.org" target="_blank" rel="noopener">joinmastodon.org</a>
        </li>
        <li>
          <a href="https://fedidb.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener">fedidb.com</a>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="bar">
      <span>joinfediverse.kr · 2024 —</span>
      <span>CC0 · 공동의 문서, 자유롭게 수정·공유</span>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>

<style>
  footer.bot {
    padding: 72px 0 40px;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--line);
    margin-top: 40px;
  }
  footer.bot .wrap {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1.6fr 1fr 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 48px;
  }
  .f-brand p {
    font-size: 14px;
    color: var(--ink-2);
    max-width: 36ch;
    line-height: 1.65;
    margin: 12px 0 0;
  }
  footer.bot h5 {
    font-family: var(--mono);
    font-size: 11.5px;
    color: var(--ink-3);
    letter-spacing: 0.06em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin: 0 0 14px;
    font-weight: 500;
  }
  footer.bot ul {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 0;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 10px;
  }
  footer.bot a {
    font-size: 14px;
    color: var(--ink-2);
  }
  footer.bot a:hover {
    color: var(--ink);
  }
  footer.bot .bar {
    grid-column: 1 / -1;
    margin-top: 40px;
    padding-top: 24px;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--line);
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    gap: 16px;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    font-family: var(--mono);
    font-size: 11.5px;
    color: var(--ink-3);
  }
  .brand {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 10px;
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 17px;
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
    text-decoration: none;
    color: var(--ink);
  }
  .brand .logo {
    width: 28px;
    height: 28px;
    border-radius: 9px;
    background:
      radial-gradient(circle at 30% 30%, var(--mint) 0 42%, transparent 43%),
      radial-gradient(circle at 72% 68%, var(--lilac) 0 30%, transparent 31%),
      var(--ink);
  }
  @media (max-width: 1024px) {
    footer.bot .wrap {
      grid-template-columns: 1.4fr 1fr 1fr;
    }
    footer.bot .f-brand {
      grid-column: 1 / -1;
    }
  }
  @media (max-width: 720px) {
    footer.bot {
      padding: 56px 0 32px;
    }
    footer.bot .wrap {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 28px;
    }
    footer.bot .f-brand {
      grid-column: 1 / -1;
    }
    footer.bot .bar {
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 8px;
      font-size: 11px;
    }
  }
</style>
